ice]] || style=\"text-align:center;\" | {{convert|132|km|mi|abbr=on}} || [[File:Mountainstage.svg|20px|alt=|link=]] || Stage with mountain(s) || {{flagathlete|[[Eugenio Gestri]]|ITA|1861}} || {{flagathlete|[[Antonin Magne]]|FRA}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1931 Tour de France, Stage 13 to Stage 24#Stage 15|15]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |17 July|| [[Nice]] to [[Gap, Hautes-Alpes|Gap]] || style=\"text-align:center;\" | {{convert|233|km|mi|abbr=on}} || [[File:Mountainstage.svg|20px|alt=|link=]] || Stage with mountain(s) || {{flagathlete|[[Jef Demuysere]]|BEL}} || {{flagathlete|[[Antonin Magne]]|FRA}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1931 Tour de France, Stage 13 to Stage 24#Stage 16|16]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |18 July|| [[Gap, Hautes-Alpes|Gap]] to [[Grenoble]] || style=\"text-align:center;\" | {{convert|102|km|mi|abbr=on}} || [[File:Mountainstage.svg|20px|alt=|link=]] || Stage with mountain(s) || {{flagathlete|[[Charles P\u00e9lissier]]|FRA}} || {{flagathlete|[[Antonin Magne]]|FRA}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1931 Tour de France, Stage 13 to Stage 24#Stage 17|17]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |19 July|| [[Grenoble]] to [[Aix-les-Bains]] || style=\"text-align:center;\" | {{convert|230|km|mi|abbr=on}} || [[File:Mountainstage.svg|20px|alt=|link=]] || Stage with mountain(s) || {{flagathlete|[[Max Bulla]]|AUT}} || {{flagathlete|[[Antonin Magne]]|FRA}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1931 Tour de France, Stage 13 to Stage 24#Stage 18|18]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |20 July|| [[Aix-les-Bains]] to [[\u00c9vian-les-Bains|Evian]] || style=\"text-align:center;\" | {{convert|204|km|mi|abbr=on}} || [[File:Mountainstage.svg|20px|alt=|link=]] || Stage with mountain(s) || {{flagathlete|[[Jef Demuysere]]|BEL}} || {{flagathlete|[[Antonin Magne]]|FRA}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1931 Tour de France, Stage 13 to Stage 24#Stage 19|19]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |21 July|| [[Evian]] to [[Belfort]] || style=\"text-align:center;\" | {{convert|282|km|mi|abbr=on}} || [[File:Mountain