Rosenborg}}<br/><small>(19 June 1972)</small>\n| lowest attendance  = 1,000<br/>{{nobreak|H\u00f8dd 0\u20131 [[Skeid Fotball|Skeid]]}}<br/><small>(15 October 1972)</small>\n| average attendance = 5,636 {{decrease}} 14.3%\n| prevseason         = [[1971 1. divisjon|1971]]\n| nextseason         = [[1973 1. divisjon|1973]]\n}}\nThe '''1972 [[Eliteserien|1. divisjon]]''' was the 27th completed season of top division [[association football|football]] in [[Norway]].\n\n==Overview==\nIt was contested by 12 teams, and [[Viking FK]] won the championship, their second league title.\n\n==Teams and locations==\n:''Note: Table lists in alphabetical order.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" border=\"1\"\n|-\n! Team\n!{{Tooltip| Ap. | Appearances in top divisions of Norwegian football}}\n! Location\n! Stadium\n|-\n| [[SK Brann|Brann]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''20'''\n| [[Bergen]]\n| [[Brann Stadion]]\n|-\n| [[Fredrikstad FK|Fredrikstad]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''27'''\n| [[Fredrikstad]]\n| [[Old Fredrikstad Stadion|Fredrikstad Stadion]]\n|-\n| [[HamKam]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''4'''\n| [[Hamar]]\n| [[Briskeby Arena|Briskeby]]\n|-\n| [[IL H\u00f8dd|H\u00f8dd]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''5'''\n| [[Ulsteinvik]]\n| [[H\u00f8ddvoll Stadion]]\n|-\n| [[Lyn Fotball|Lyn]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''19'''\n| [[Oslo]]\n| [[Ullevaal Stadion]]\n|-\n| [[FK Mj\u00f8lner|Mj\u00f8lner]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''1'''\n| [[Narvik]]\n| Narvik Stadion\n|-\n| [[Mj\u00f8ndalen IF|Mj\u00f8ndalen]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''6'''\n| [[Mj\u00f8ndalen]]\n| [[Nedre Eiker Stadion]]\n|-\n| [[Rosenborg BK|Rosenborg]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''10'''\n| [[Trondheim]]\n| [[Lerkendal Stadion]]\n|-\n| [[Sarpsborg FK]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''22'''\n| [[Sarpsborg]]\n| [[Sarpsborg Stadion]]\n|-\n| [[Skeid Fotball|Skeid]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''25'''\n| [[Oslo]]\n| [[Bislett Stadion]]\n|-\n| [[Str\u00f8msgodset Toppfotball|Str\u00f8msgodset]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''7'''\n| [[Drammen]]\n| [[Marienlyst Stadion]]\n|-\n| [[Viking FK|Viking]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''25'''\n| [[Stavanger]]\n| [[Stavanger Stadion]]\n|}\n\n==League table==\n<onlyinclude>{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=QR\n|winpoints=2\n\n|team1=VIK|name_VIK=[[Viking FK|Viking]]\n|team2=FFK|name_FFK=[[Fredrikstad FK|Fredrikstad]]\n|team3=STR|name_STR=[[Str\u00f8msgodset IF|Str\u00f8msgodset]]\n|team4=ROS|name_ROS=[[Rosenborg BK|Rosenborg]]\n|team5=LYN|name_LYN=[[FK Lyn|Lyn]]\n|team6=SKD|name_SKD=[[Skeid Fotball|Skeid]]\n|team7=MIF|name_MIF=[[Mj\u00f8ndalen IF|Mj\u00f8ndalen]]\n|team8=BRA|name_BRA=[[SK Brann|Brann]]\n|team9=HAM|name_HAM=[[HamKam]]\n|team10=SRP|name_SRP=[[Sarpsborg FK]]\n|team11=H\u00d8D|name_H\u00d8D=[[IL H\u00f8dd|H\u00f8dd]]\n|team12=MJ\u00d8|name_MJ\u00d8=[[FK Mj\u00f8lner|Mj\u00f8lner]]\n\n|win_VIK=16|draw_VIK=2|loss_VIK=4|gf_VIK=42|ga_VIK=15|status_VIK=C\n|win_FFK=16|draw_FFK=2|loss_FFK=4|gf_FFK=31|ga_FFK=16\n|win_STR=10|draw_STR=7|loss_STR=5|gf_STR=40|ga_STR=29\n|win_ROS=6|draw_ROS=10|loss_ROS=6|gf_ROS=22|ga_ROS=19\n|win_LYN=7|draw_LYN=7|loss_LYN=8|gf_LYN=29|ga_LYN=22\n|win_SKD=8|draw_SKD=5|loss_SKD=9|gf_SKD=26|ga_SKD=26\n|win_MIF=9|draw_MIF=3|loss_MIF=10|gf_MIF=31|ga_MIF=36\n|win_BRA=7|draw_BRA=6|loss_BRA=9|gf_BRA=22|ga_BRA=23\n|win_HAM=6|draw_HAM=8|loss_HAM=8|gf_HAM=14|ga_HAM=18\n|win_SRP=6|draw_SRP=6|loss_SRP=10|gf_SRP=21|ga_SRP=30|status_SRP=R\n|win_H\u00d8D=4|draw_H\u00d8D=6|loss_H\u00d8D=12|gf_H\u00d8D=18|ga_H\u00d8D=39|status_H\u00d8D=R\n|win_MJ\u00d8=3|draw_MJ\u00d8=6|loss_MJ\u00d8=13|gf_MJ\u00d8=10|ga_MJ\u00d8=33|status_MJ\u00d8=R\n\n|col_EC1=green1|text_EC1=Qualification for the [[1973\u201374 European Cup|European Cup first round]]\n|result1=EC1\n|col_UC1=blue1|text_UC1=Qualification for the [[1973\u201374 UEFA Cup|UEFA Cup first round]]\n|result2=UC1|result3=UC1\n|col_ECWC1=#FFEBAD|text_ECWC1=Qualification for the [[1973\u201374 European Cup Winners' Cup|Cup Winners' Cup first round]]\n|result8=ECWC1\n|col_R=red1|text_R=Relegation to [[1973 2. divisjon|2. divisjon]]\n|result10=R|